description:
Portugal Weather Stations data (from 01 Jan 2016 to 01 Jan 2019). Parameters: 
- air temperature (degrees Celsius) at 2 metre height above the earth's surface;
- atmospheric pressure at weather station level (millimeters of mercury);
- atmospheric pressure reduced to mean sea level (millimeters of mercury); 
- relative humidity (%) at a height of 2 metres above the earth's surface;
Time-Frequency from 30 minutes to 3 hours
- timestamp format: DD.MM.YYYY HH:MM
- Interval: 01.01.16-01.01.2019
Stations: 8544_Ovar; 8561_beja; 8551_Castelo_do_Neiva; 8575_braganca; 8570_castelo_branco; 8548_coimbra; 8558_evora; 8554_faro, 8568_Penhas_Douradas; 8540_Monte_Real; 8579_Lisbon; 8571_portalegre; 8545_porto; 8537_Alverca; 8534_Montijo; 8567_Vila_Real; 8560_viseu; 8541_sines
